461
00:38:25,519 --> 00:38:28,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sve to treba uništiti, tradiciju, tradicionalne odnose, sve,

462
00:38:28,519 --> 00:38:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] i onda će biti raj na zemlji.

463
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek je nastaje opakao.

464
00:38:32,739 --> 00:38:36,639
