548
00:42:34,579 --> 00:42:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nije, kako je to cijepivo?

549
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ni te štiti od bolesti,

550
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,179
[SPEAKER_01] ni te zaustavlja prenošenje bolesti

551
00:42:39,179 --> 00:42:40,780
